{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>定义0的后继为1，证明对于任何自然数都有a*1 = a</h1>\n<p>根据乘法定义\na<em>b′ = a</em>b+a\na<em>0 = 0\n所以\na</em>1=a*0+a=a</p>\n<h1>证明乘法结合律和交换律</h1>\n<p>结合律\n(a<em>b)</em>c = a<em>(b</em>c)\n图形证明:给定长宽高的立方体 将其翻转不会影响其体积</p>\n<p>交换律\na<em>b = b</em>a\n图形证明:给定长宽高的长方形 将其旋转不会影响其面积</p>\n<h1>证明乘法分配律</h1>\n<p>(a+b)<em>c = a</em>c + b*c</p>","fields":{"slug":"/baseball/编程的数学原理/1-1/","disqus":{"shortname":"woodgear-blog"}},"frontmatter":{"id":"uazdpsm","time":"1996-09-08T23:37:07+08:00","tag":null},"parent":{"__typename":"File","name":"1-1","ext":".md","birthTime":"2020-08-12T15:37:07.057Z","changeTime":"2020-08-12T17:06:21.594Z","relativeDirectory":"baseball/编程的数学原理","absolutePath":"/home/oaa/temp/blog/baseball/编程的数学原理/1-1.md"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/baseball/编程的数学原理/1-1/","disqus":{"shortname":"woodgear-blog"}}}